title: Stand-Up Comedy On Late Night
description:
Amber Ruffin and Jenny Hagel help out with some Jokes Seth Can't Tell.

Then, some stand-up comedy sets from comics who have appeared on Late Night: Josh Gondelman, Zainab Johnson, Julio Torres, Naomi Ekperigin and Nimesh Patel.
